swp_compiler_ss13.common.ast.nodes.unary

Interface StructIdentifierNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ASTNode, ExpressionNode, IdentifierNode, StatementNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StructIdentifierNodeImpl

    public interface StructIdentifierNode
extends IdentifierNode
    The node to reference a struct field. The fieldname defines the field to access. The identifier itself is another IdentifierNode. This IdentifierNode can be a BasicIdentifierNode to access the first struct level. It can be another ArrayIdentifierNode to access a multidimensional array or a StructIdentifierNode to access a struct inside a struct.
    Author:
    "Frank Zechert"
